
    Run only wmr-oregon software is alarm enabled

make directory /etc/wmr/script/
copy wmr.conf /etc/wmr/
cpopy & edit all sensor named script in ./etc/wmr/script/ to /etc/wmr/script/
copy this script to /usr/bin/wmr_alarm.sh
edit /etc/wmr/wmr.conf - lines:
ALARMENABLE 1
ALARMBIN /usr/bin/wmr_alarm.sh

Alarm event enable.
